As you should know the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) grants a number of protections to individuals:

https://gdpr-info.eu/

Consider this a formal complaint and request to immediately remove my contact information, and any other identifying information about myself from your systems.

Additionally I revoke your permission to sell, transfer, or otherwise share my information going forward.

Please respond acknowledging your receipt and compliance with this request. If you are unable to comply with this action directly, please provide the contact for GDPR requests, or forward this to said contact.

If you do not comply with this request, rest assured I will be filing a complaint with the European Data Protection Supervisor.
